desc:
55% boost to all parameters of Light, Dark types, enormously boosts Light, Dark elemental damage, enormously boosts OD gauge fill rate & 10% damage reduction from Light, Dark types
Guild Raid: Boosts Atk, Def when BB gauge is over 50% & adds Extra Skill disable effects purge to UBB
lore: A beautifully gilded medal set with fine amethyst and precious silver. It glows with the mystical energy of an otherworldly twilight, a realm between sun and shadow. Grants its bearer great power over light and darkness.
name: Duskcrown Medal
